71
17^2=289
289=4\cdot71+5
17^{14}=(17^2)^7=289^7\equiv 5^7\pmod {71}
5^4=625
9\cdot71=639
625=639-14
5^4\equiv -14\pmod{71}
5^5\equiv -70\equiv 1\pmod{71}
17^{14}\equiv 5^7\equiv 5^2\equiv 25 \pmod{71}\;.
